OL,3,CMum spared jail for inciting racial
OL,4,Chatred with online post amid national
OL,5,Criots
OL,7,FA west Cumbrian mum has been given a
OL,8,Fsuspended prison sentence for inciting
OL,9,Fracial hatred with a social media post
OL,10,Famid national riots and unrest
OL,11,Ffollowing the fatal Southport
OL,12,Fstabbings.
OL,14,FMegan Morrison, 27, shared an image on
OL,15,Fher Facebook page which showed violent
OL,16,Fdisorder at a Holiday Inn in Rotherham
OL,17,Fhousing asylum seekers who were left
OL,18,Ffearing for their lives.
