OL,7,FCarlisle Crown Court heard on 7 March
OL,8,Fthat Morrison, of Mona Road,
OL,9,FSalterbeck, added a caption which
OL,10,Fread: "They should do this to the
OL,11,FCumberland Hotel. It's full of them."
OL,13,FProsecutor Tim Evans told the court:
OL,14,F"There was an immediate response from
OL,15,Fa friend or follower of the defendant
OL,16,Fwho commented 'Megan, you can't incite
OL,17,Friots ffs!'.
