OL,7,F"Her response to that was extremely
OL,8,Ftroubling and highly illustrative at
OL,9,Fthis time of national tension. To her
OL,10,Ffriend, she responded with a laughing
OL,11,Femoji, rather than the horror followed
OL,12,Fby the immediate withdrawal of the
OL,13,Fpost, which is, of course, what right-
OL,14,Fthinking citizens would do."
OL,16,FMr Evans said there were no asylum
OL,17,Fseekers being housed at the Cumberland
OL,18,FHotel, nor had any ever been housed
OL,19,Fthere.
