OL,7,F"But this is, of course, the terrible
OL,8,Fdanger of these criminally ill-advised
OL,9,Fposting," suggested Mr Evans.
OL,10,F"Entirely innocent people or
OL,11,Fproperties can be dragged into
OL,12,Fsituations by this sort of invitation
OL,13,Fif people accept."
OL,15,FMorrison's post came on 6 August `
OL,16,Fjust eight days after three children
OL,17,Fwere murdered and 10 others injured at
OL,18,Fa Taylor Swift-themed dance class in
OL,19,FSouthport.
