OL,4,Chatred with online post amid national
OL,5,Criots
OL,7,FA woman with no previous convictions,
OL,8,FMorrison was one of a number of people
OL,9,Fprosecuted across Cumbria for racially
OL,10,Foffensive online posts. She later
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to a charge of inciting
OL,12,Fracial hatred.
OL,14,FDuring today's sentencing hearing,
OL,15,FMorrison's barrister said her phone
OL,16,Fhad been seized by police. She had not
OL,17,Freplaced it and she had since
OL,18,Fwithdrawn from any use of social media
OL,19,Fas part of what he called her "self-
OL,20,Frehabilitation".
