OL,7,FShe told a probation officer who
OL,8,Fprepared a pre-sentence report that
OL,9,Fher offending was "stupid".
OL,11,F"Indeed it was," said Judge Nicholas
OL,12,FBarker as he passed sentence. After
OL,13,Fhearing details of Morrison's family
OL,14,Fcircumstances and accepting her
OL,15,Fgenuine remorse, the judge suspended a
OL,16,Fsix-month jail term for 18 months.
