OL,7,FSpeaking about the Rotherham hotel
OL,8,Friot post share, Judge Barker told
OL,9,FMorrison: "What you did was to
OL,10,Fdemonstrate an implied assertion that
OL,11,Fyou supported the actions that these
OL,12,Fmindless thugs were taking."
OL,14,FThe judge added: "No one considering
OL,15,Fthis case can themselves disconnect it
OL,16,Ffrom the wave of civil disorder,
OL,17,Fappalling conduct, that swept this
OL,18,Fcountry in the summer month of August
OL,19,Flast year. You were part of that."
